callRobberMethodsByAKnightCard() - Method in class shared.facades.RobberFacade
This method is activated by playing a Soldier Development card and calls the RobberFacade.moveRobber(HexLocation, HexLocation) and RobberFacade.stealFrom(Player, Player), in left-to-right order Note: The RobberFacade.discardHalf(Player) will not be called with this method
callRobberMethodsByRollingA7() - Method in class shared.facades.RobberFacade
This method is activated by rolling a 7 and calls the RobberFacade.discardHalf(Player), RobberFacade.moveRobber(HexLocation, HexLocation), and RobberFacade.stealFrom(Player, Player), in left-to-right order Note: RobberFacade.discardHalf(Player) will be called for each individual Player in the ClientModel
